    "Each drive is formatted as FAT32 (volume label WINSETUP) and receives the Windows installer. Requires install.wim or install.esd and wimlib-imagex (brew install wimlib)." : {
      "extractionState" : "stale",
      "localizations" : {
        "ar" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "يتم تنسيق كل محرك أقراص بتنسيق FAT32 (تسمية وحدة التخزين WINSETUP) ويتلقى مثبت Windows. يتطلب install.wim أو install.esd وwimlib-imagex (تثبيت الشراب wimlib)."
          }
        },
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Each drive is formatted as FAT32 (volume label WINSETUP) and receives the Windows installer. Requires install.wim or install.esd and wimlib-imagex (brew install wimlib)."
          }
        },
        "es" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Cada unidad está formateada como FAT32 (etiqueta de volumen WINSETUP) y recibe el instalador de Windows. Requiere install.wim o install.esd y wimlib-imagex (brew install wimlib)."
          }
        },
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Chaque disque est formaté en FAT32 (nom de volume WINSETUP) et reçoit le programme d'installation de Windows. Nécessite install.wim ou install.esd et wimlib-imagex (brew install wimlib)."
          }
        },
        "he" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Each drive is formatted as FAT32 (volume label WINSETUP) and receives the Windows installer. Requires install.wim or install.esd and wimlib-imagex (brew install wimlib)."
          }
        },
        "hi" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "प्रत्येक ड्राइव को FAT32 (वॉल्यूम लेबल WinSETUP) के रूप में स्वरूपित किया जाता है और Windows इंस्टॉलर प्राप्त होता है। install.wim या install.esd और wimlib-imagex (brew install wimlib) की आवश्यकता है।"
          }
