    "The catalog loads in the background. Tap Choose to pick an installer." : {

    },
    "The converter script ships with the app; CLI tools are still required at runtime. Release builds bundle them under Resources/Tools/bin. When building from source, run Scripts/bundle-mac-cli-tools.sh (Homebrew on the dev machine) or install packages manually:" : {
      "extractionState" : "stale",
      "localizations" : {
        "ar" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "يأتي البرنامج النصي للمحول مع التطبيق؛ لا تزال أدوات CLI مطلوبة في وقت التشغيل. يتم تجميع إصدارات الإصدار ضمن الموارد/الأدوات/الحاوية. عند البناء من المصدر، قم بتشغيل Scripts/bundle-mac-cli-tools.sh (Homebrew على جهاز التطوير) أو قم بتثبيت الحزم يدويًا:"
          }
        },
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "The converter script ships with the app; CLI tools are still required at runtime. Release builds bundle them under Resources/Tools/bin. When building from source, run Scripts/bundle-mac-cli-tools.sh (Homebrew on the dev machine) or install packages manually:"
          }
        },
        "es" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "El script del convertidor se envía con la aplicación; Las herramientas CLI aún son necesarias en tiempo de ejecución. Las versiones de lanzamiento las agrupan en Recursos/Herramientas/bin. Al compilar desde el código fuente, ejecute Scripts/bundle-mac-cli-tools.sh (Homebrew en la máquina de desarrollo) o instale los paquetes manualmente:"
          }
        },
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "The converter script ships with the app; CLI tools are still required at runtime. Release builds bundle them under Resources/Tools/bin. When building from source, run Scripts/bundle-mac-cli-tools.sh (Homebrew on the dev machine) or install packages manually:"
          }
        },
        "he" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "The converter script ships with the app; CLI tools are still required at runtime. Release builds bundle them under Resources/Tools/bin. When building from source, run Scripts/bundle-mac-cli-tools.sh (Homebrew on the dev machine) or install packages manually:"
          }
        },
        "hi" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "कनवर्टर स्क्रिप्ट ऐप के साथ आती है; रनटाइम पर सीएलआई उपकरण अभी भी आवश्यक हैं। रिलीज़ बिल्ड उन्हें संसाधन/टूल्स/बिन के अंतर्गत बंडल करता है। स्रोत से निर्माण करते समय, Scripts/bundle-mac-cli-tools.sh (डेव मशीन पर Homebrew) चलाएँ या मैन्युअल रूप से पैकेज स्थापित करें:"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "The converter script ships with the app; CLI tools are still required at runtime. Release builds bundle them under Resources/Tools/bin. When building from source, run Scripts/bundle-mac-cli-tools.sh (Homebrew on the dev machine) or install packages manually:"
          }
        }
      }
